      "rationale": "The SST k-omega turbulence model and the Giersiepen-Wurzinger hemolysis power-law model are the most widely used formulations for centrifugal blood pump CFD in the literature. Model form uncertainty is acknowledged but formal assessment is not required at MRL 2. Selection rationale is documented."
